{"tid":608963,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"悟空很忙！東映動畫將為《龍珠》成立專屬部門！","createTime":"2018-03-28T15:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T14:26:02.000Z","uid":25345,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"86d024c30d9d2d8b665361c355da0eb3b7f352cc","tid":608963,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201803/26/0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201803%2F26%2F0.jpg&h=f163e644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n野澤雅子都81歲啦<br />\n成套龍珠悟空都係佢一人配<br />\n佢唔係度既話,日本人鬼接受到另一個悟空聲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由鳥山明創作的國民級作品《龍珠》儘管距離原作完結已經過去20多年的時間，但官方依然會不斷推出新的企劃。<br />\n<br />\n因為粉絲們始終保持的熱情，也讓官方從未忽視這個超級IP的影響力。近日有消息指，東映動畫成立了專門負責《龍珠》的部門！<br />\n<br />\n在3月23日的時候，東映動畫公佈了組織架構和人事變更的消息。其中在TV企劃部方面，東映新增設了一個名為第三視頻企劃部的部門，這個部門的主要任務就是負責《龍珠》。該部門的負責人為鈴木篤志。看來這個IP冷飯太好炒了！"},{"pid":"c6024f4ea3fae1ee14a37a6c1bb5f8c8bb204ad9","tid":608963,"uid":60831,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"原來已經81歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個人配晒悟空，悟飯，悟天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb68cbb715f0075fe7d27754b4eb8d8bca4a2b09","tid":608963,"uid":37528,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"quote":{"pid":"c6024f4ea3fae1ee14a37a6c1bb5f8c8bb204ad9","tid":608963,"uid":60831,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"原來已經81歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個人配晒悟空，悟飯，悟天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T16:09:51.000Z","msg":"仲有悟空